    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2008 Porsche Cayman S (987.1), a superlative example of mid-engine engineering. This specimen features the M97.21 3.4L flat-six powerplant, delivering linear torque via VarioCam Plus. The 6-speed manual transaxle shifts with surgical precision, benefiting from a recently inspected dual-mass flywheel. Mechanically, the vehicle is flawless; a recent borescope inspection confirmed zero cylinder bore scoring, and the rear main seal remains bone dry. The chassis is equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), providing a lowered ride height and adaptive damping for optimized roll stiffness. The exterior retains its factory-applied finish with no evidence of thermal cycling fatigue on the plastics or oxidation on the undercarriage components. Interior bolsters and switchgear are devoid of the typical soft-touch wear, preserving the original tactile feedback. For the enthusiast seeking a high-revving, naturally aspirated analog experience with documented provenance.",
      "price": 47500.0,
